    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth, dependable ride that you can count on. It\u2019s a wonderful choice for anyone looking for a reliable and comfortable vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
