      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising standards. This specimen maintains a showroom-grade aesthetic and mechanical integrity that defies its tenure on the road. Meticulously preserved and rigorously inspected, it represents the pinnacle of its class for the discerning collector or enthusiast. An investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
